snippet.title: Finding the Sum of a Finite Arithmetic Series
snippet.description:
Thanks to all of you who support me on Patreon. You da real mvps!   $1 per month helps!! :)  https://www.patreon.com/patrickjmt !! Finding the Sum of a Finite Arithmetic Series.
In this video, I show two formulas to find the sum of a finite arithmetic series and do two examples of finding some sums!
